* Aḥmad b. Ḥanbal, &quot;Kitāb al-ṣalāh&quot; (with a supplement comprising Ibn Qayyim al-Jawziyya&#x27;s &quot;al-Ṣalāh wa-aḥkām tārikīhā&quot;), ed. Zakariyyā ʿAlī Yusūf, Cairo 1971
