* Marʿī b. Yūsuf al-Karmī, &quot;al-Shahāda al-zakiyya fī thanāʾ al-aʾimma ʿalā Ibn Taymiyya&quot;, ed. Najm ʿAbd al-Raḥmān Khalaf, Beirut 1404/1984
