* 1st Tadeusz Kościuszko Infantry Division, a Second World War unit, part of the 1st Polish Army
* 111th Fighter Escadrille (Poland), known as Kościuszko&#x27;s squadron, was a Polish fighter squadron in the Invasion of Poland of 1939
